      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish remains flawless, retaining its original deep luster with no swirls, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and the 'new car' scent is still present. Every electronic component, switch, and dial functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean history, this is the finest specimen available for a discerning collector who demands perfection. Inspection by a specialist is welcomed and encouraged to verify its pristine state.",
